    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事背景</h2>我们穿梭于宇宙之中，收集珍贵的宝物。在旅途中我们享受着宇宙的瑰丽景色，也会遭遇不同的敌人，我们会制造黑洞并且吞噬我们的敌人。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2>这是一款简单轻松的游戏，当您选择两个相同颜色的目标时，它们会被闪电连接起来然后被黑洞销毁。当您销毁100个目标时，您就通关了。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214860/extras/7483a3954f74e80af1ff340fbc4f4169.poster.avif?t=1670630705\" width=720 height=418 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214860/extras/7483a3954f74e80af1ff340fbc4f4169.webm?t=1670630705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214860/extras/7483a3954f74e80af1ff340fbc4f4169.mp4?t=1670630705\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>当然，您要在规定时间内完成才能通关，每个关卡限时5分钟，时间越短您获得的评价越高。正如我所说的这是一款简单解压的小游戏。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214860/extras/43d6af449959c3f268bd89daf05503e4.poster.avif?t=1670630705\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214860/extras/43d6af449959c3f268bd89daf05503e4.webm?t=1670630705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214860/extras/43d6af449959c3f268bd89daf05503e4.mp4?t=1670630705\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2>为了让游戏更加有趣，我将游戏制作成3D画面。不同于传统的2D画面，您可以操作角色自由地飞行在宇宙中，不会被限制。在飞行的过程中您需要不断地连接更多的目标，您很快就会发现其中的乐趣。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >更多的游戏模式</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >障碍物模式：添加随机数量的物体，它们跟目标有着相同大小和颜色，但是选择它们不会有任何反应。</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214860/extras/fcf6f53e13393dae1ac0ef00c81061ab.poster.avif?t=1670630705\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214860/extras/fcf6f53e13393dae1ac0ef00c81061ab.webm?t=1670630705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214860/extras/fcf6f53e13393dae1ac0ef00c81061ab.mp4?t=1670630705\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >宝石模式：在消除100个目标的基础上，收集随机指定的宝石数量才能通关。</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214860/extras/4f62a41240ea2caef08efbd62d477bdc.poster.avif?t=1670630705\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214860/extras/4f62a41240ea2caef08efbd62d477bdc.webm?t=1670630705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214860/extras/4f62a41240ea2caef08efbd62d477bdc.mp4?t=1670630705\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >消失模式：目标会随机消失，当目标越来越少的时候，您很难锁定它。</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214860/extras/39ad27fa6d9bd27e64448e28a2202c44.poster.avif?t=1670630705\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214860/extras/39ad27fa6d9bd27e64448e28a2202c44.webm?t=1670630705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214860/extras/39ad27fa6d9bd27e64448e28a2202c44.mp4?t=1670630705\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >这些游戏模式会干扰您快速选择目标，想要满分通关可不容易。</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >更多好玩的</h2>随着胜利的次数越来越多，会为您解锁新的地图。在新的地图里会生成Boss，拥有不同的技能，随时会向您发起攻击。你需要及时地躲避Boss的技能，因为您如果被击中，那么您的角色会立刻死亡，需要重新挑战。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214860/extras/90c6bce39a1e50cbf84876990b82801e.poster.avif?t=1670630705\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214860/extras/90c6bce39a1e50cbf84876990b82801e.webm?t=1670630705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214860/extras/90c6bce39a1e50cbf84876990b82801e.mp4?t=1670630705\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >目前游戏内已经有4场地图，800个关卡等待您的解锁。</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开发者想说</h2>这是我第一款开发的独立游戏，我希望能把这游戏越做越好。所以希望各位玩家们体验完后能够对这款游戏有所评价，我会尽我所能更好的完善它。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >您可以联系我</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >QQ：690845098</h2>",
